						               													<description>Fueled by climate change, millions upon millions of minions are set to disrupt the way we live on Planet Earth: Carbions build up Disruption Scale as our reliance on oil, plastics, and the like grew; Climmies descend to organizations and communities everywhere and causes disruptions to our normal way of working and living. Some of the minions are bound for your organization. These wicked creatures are mischievous and unpredictable, The only way to bring the minions under control is to activate Zillians, the resilience superheros who provide the ultimate resilience any organization can wish for a sustainable future.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Minions of Disruptions, you and your fellow players are colleagues from the same organization or neighbors from the same community to combat climate minions. You must work hard and smart together to activate resilience superheros, Zillians, before the two types of minions, carbions and climmies, take over with their disruptions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Minions of Disruptions is designed to be played by multiple teams, and can also be played standalone by one single team.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Visit website: dayad.org/game-day for more information!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
